    <h1>Information about Bonus points</h1>
<p>
    When you make a purchase of a specific room, the amount of bonus points you receive will be the price of the room x10.
    For example, if you purchase a family room for 750 kr, you will then receive 7500 bonus points.
</p>
<p>
    When you have saved up enough bonus points you can use them to purchase rooms.
    The price of a room when purchasing them with bonus points are the price of the room x100.
    For example, a family room will cost 75 000 points.
</p>
<p>
    If you choose to purchase the room buy credit card you will instantly get the bonus points added to your account. If
    you choose to pay upon arrival you will receive the points when you pay at the desk.
</p>
